          2. Taxes are not incurred when exchanging annuities, as long as the exchange is in compliance with section 1035 of the Internal Revenue Code.
	
    

          3. According to 12/31/15 data on non-group open variable annuities from Morningstar, Inc., at 0.25% Fidelity Personal Retirement Annuity's annual annuity charge is significantly lower than the national industry average 1.25% annual annuity charge. Underlying fund fees also apply.
	
    

